cite_note-8\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\" style=\"pointer-events: none;\">[</span>8<span class=\"cite-bracket\" style=\"pointer-events: none;\">]</span></a></sup></p>', 'fsfs sfr fb ggt fsdg', '[\"Business Strategy\",\"Courier\",\"Design and Creative\"]', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dcrk1fzah/image/upload/v1742192517/blog_images/hk0adhb0dv16drfdudnc.jpg', 13, '2025-03-17 06:21:59', 'digital marketing strategies', 'digital-marketing-strategies-small-business-2024', 'Digital marketing strategies diagram for small businesses 2024');
