(32, 'Apple MacBook Pro A1502 13.3-inch Laptop (Intel Core i5/8GB/256GB SSD/Mac OS/Integrated Graphics), Silver', 'Laptop', 23645.00, 'The Apple MacBook Pro A1502 (Refurbished)\r\n \r\nThe Apple MacBook Pro A1502 refers to a specific model of MacBook Pro, which was released in October 2013 and was part of the Retina display MacBook Pro series. Here are the specifications for the MacBook Pro A1502 from that time:\r\nDisplay:\r\n13.3-inch Retina display with a resolution of 2560 x 1600 pixels. This display featured vibrant colors and high resolution.\r\nProcessor:\r\nDepending on the configuration, it could be equipped with a dual-core Intel Core i5 or Core i7 processor. These processors were from the Haswell generation.\r\nGraphics:\r\nIntegrated Intel Iris Graphics 5100.\r\nMemory (RAM):\r\nOptions for 4GB or 8GB of DDR3L RAM.\r\nStorage:\r\nDifferent configurations were available with various storage options, including 128GB, 256GB, and 512GB PCIe-based flash storage. Some higher-end configurations had 1TB of storage.\r\nPorts:\r\n2 x USB 3.0 ports\r\n2 x Thunderbolt 2 ports\r\n1 x HDMI port\r\n1 x SDXC card slot\r\n1 x 3.5mm headphone jack\r\nMagSafe 2 power port\r\nWireless:\r\n802.11ac Wi-Fi\r\nBluetooth 4.0\r\nOperating System:\r\nIt was originally shipped with macOS Mavericks (10.9) but was capable of running later macOS versions.\r\nBattery Life:\r\nApple claimed up to 9 hours of web browsing or up to 9 hours of iTunes movie playback on a single charge.\r\nDimensions and Weight:\r\nHeight: 0.71 inches (1.8 cm)\r\nWidth: 12.35 inches (31.4 cm)\r\nDepth: 8.62 inches (21.9 cm)\r\nWeight: Approximately 3.46 pounds (1.57 kg)\r\nWarranty:\r\n   1 month Testing \r\n', '9876568890', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dswzvbhix/image/upload/v1740653349/e0yewc96bnydjupjv1yk.png', '2025-02-27 10:49:09'),
(33, 'Apple Macbook Pro A2141(2019) i7-9th Gen-32gb ram-500gb ssd-16″ Display', 'Laptop', 50000.00, 'Apple MacBook Pro A2141 (2019) – Power and Performance Redefined\r\n\r\nExperience unparalleled performance and premium design with the Apple MacBook Pro A2141 (2019). This powerhouse is designed for professionals who demand speed, reliability, and cutting-edge technology.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n1. 9th Generation Intel Core i7 Processor\r\n\r\nPowered by the 9th Gen Intel Core i7, this MacBook Pro delivers lightning-fast performance, making it ideal for multitasking, complex computations, and demanding applications.\r\n2. 32GB RAM\r\n\r\nWith 32GB of RAM, enjoy seamless performance even when running multiple high-demand programs or virtual machines.\r\n3. 500GB SSD Storage\r\n\r\nThe lightning-fast 500GB SSD ensures quick boot times, swift application launches, and ample storage for your essential files and projects.\r\n4. Stunning 16-Inch Retina Display\r\n\r\nThe brilliant 16-inch Retina display with True Tone technology offers vibrant colors, deep contrasts, and razor-sharp text—perfect for creatives, editors, and designers.\r\n5. macOS Compatibility\r\n\r\nPreloaded with macOS, the MacBook Pro delivers a smooth, intuitive experience and access to powerful productivity tools and creative software.\r\n6. Sleek and Durable Design\r\n\r\nCrafted with Apple’s signature unibody aluminum chassis, this laptop combines style and durability in a lightweight, portable package.\r\n7. Advanced Graphics\r\n\r\nEquipped with powerful graphics capabilities, this MacBook Pro is ready to handle graphic-intensive tasks like video editing, 3D rendering, and gaming.\r\nWhy Choose the Apple MacBook Pro A2141 (2019)?\r\nDesigned for professionals who need top-tier performance and reliability.\r\nPerfect for video editing, coding, graphic design, and other resource-intensive tasks.\r\nBacked by Apple’s commitment to innovation and user-friendly design.\r\nTake your productivity and creativity to the next level with the Apple MacBook Pro A2141. Upgrade to unmatched power and performance today!', '9876568890', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dswzvbhix/image/upload/v1740653800/falsgrvchyue4oooct4y.png', '2025-02-27 10:56:40'),
(34, 'Dell Gaming G15-5530 13th Gen/i5-13450HX/16GB/512GB SSD', 'Laptop', 104952.00, 'Dell Gaming G15-5530 Laptop – High-Performance Gaming Machine\r\n\r\nThe Dell Gaming G15-5530 is a powerful gaming laptop designed for an immersive gaming experience. Featuring a 15.6-inch display, it comes in a sleek Dark Shadow Gray finish with a black thermal shelf for efficient cooling.\r\n\r\nPerformance & Memory\r\nProcessor: Intel Core i5 (3.4 GHz)\r\nRAM: 16GB DDR5 (expandable up to 32GB)\r\nStorage: 512GB SSD for fast boot-ups and load times\r\nGraphics & Display\r\nGraphics Card: NVIDIA Dedicated 6GB GDDR6 GPU\r\nScreen Size: 15.6 inches, offering a crisp visual experience\r\nConnectivity & Ports\r\nWi-Fi: High-speed connectivity\r\nUSB Ports: 3 (2 x USB 3.0, 1 x USB 2.0)\r\nOther Ports: HDMI, USB, headphone jack\r\nBattery & Power\r\nBattery Life: Up to 8.5 hours\r\nPower Source: Battery-powered (3-cell lithium-ion)\r\nAdditional Features\r\nOperating System: Pre-installed Windows 11 Home\r\nWeight: 2.65 kg, making it a solid yet portable gaming laptop\r\nIncluded Components: Laptop, battery, AC adapter, user guide, and manuals\r\nThe Dell Gaming G15-5530 is an excellent choice for gamers and professionals looking for high performance, powerful graphics, and reliable battery life. Whether gaming or multitasking, this laptop ensures seamless and lag-free performance.', '9876568890', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dswzvbhix/image/upload/v1740654153/poffhvuvsfssbbzrm7wz.png', '2025-02-27 11:02:34'),
(35, 'Dell Inspiron 3511 Laptop, Core I5 Processor/ 11th/8GB/ 512GB SSD..', 'Laptop', 62000.00, 'Dell Inspiron 3511 Laptop – Sleek & Powerful for Everyday Use\r\n\r\nThe Dell Inspiron 3511 is a stylish and reliable laptop designed for smooth performance in work, study, and entertainment. With a 15.6-inch Full HD display, a backlit keyboard, and a lightweight build, it delivers both portability and efficiency.\r\n\r\nPerformance & Memory\r\nProcessor: Intel Core i5-1135G7 (2.4 GHz)\r\nRAM: 8GB DDR4 (expandable up to 32GB)\r\nStorage: 512GB SSD for fast and seamless operations\r\nDisplay & Graphics\r\nScreen Size: 15.6 inches FHD (1920 x 1080 pixels)\r\nGraphics: Intel integrated graphics with PCI Express interface\r\nConnectivity & Ports\r\nWireless: Wi-Fi (802.11ac), Bluetooth\r\nUSB Ports: 3 (USB 3.2 supported)\r\nOther Ports: HDMI, headphone jack\r\nBattery & Power\r\nBattery Life: Long-lasting lithium-ion battery\r\nPower Source: Battery-powered (240V support)\r\nAdditional Features\r\nOperating System: Windows 11 (pre-installed)\r\nSoftware: Microsoft Office 365 included\r\nKeyboard: Backlit keyboard for better visibility\r\nWeight: 1.8 kg, making it lightweight and easy to carry\r\nThe Dell Inspiron 3511 is a perfect laptop for students, professionals, and home users looking for a blend of power, portability, and productivity. Whether for office work, study, or entertainment, it ensures a smooth and efficient experience.', '9876568890', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dswzvbhix/image/upload/v1740654579/q9rurzhsgwpapfj7kees.png', '2025-02-27 11:09:39'),
(36, 'Dell Inspiron 3520,12th Gen Intel Core i5 Processor, 8GB, 512GB SSD)', 'Desktop', 66824.00, 'Dell Inspiron 3520 Laptop – Power & Performance for Everyday Use\r\n\r\nThe Dell Inspiron 3520 is a well-balanced laptop designed for productivity, entertainment, and multitasking. Featuring a 15.6-inch Full HD LED display, a powerful Intel processor, and a lightweight design, it delivers smooth performance for work, study, and casual gaming.\r\n\r\nPerformance & Memory\r\nProcessor: Intel Core i5-1235U (3.3 GHz)\r\nRAM: 8GB DDR4 (expandable up to 16GB)\r\nStorage: 512GB SSD for fast boot-up and data access\r\nDisplay & Graphics\r\nScreen Size: 15.6 inches FHD (1920 x 1080 pixels)\r\nGraphics: Intel UHD Integrated Graphics\r\nConnectivity & Ports\r\nWireless: Wi-Fi (802.11ac), Bluetooth\r\nUSB Ports: 3 (USB & HDMI supported)\r\nOther Features: Numeric Keypad for easy data entry\r\nBattery & Power\r\nBattery Life: Up to 4 hours with lithium-ion battery\r\nPower Source: Battery-powered (240V support)\r\nAdditional Features\r\nOperating System: Windows 10 (pre-installed)\r\nSoftware: Microsoft Office 365 included\r\nKeyboard: Traditional design with a numeric keypad\r\nWeight: 1.65 kg, making it portable and lightweight\r\nThe Dell Inspiron 3520 is an excellent choice for students, professionals, and casual users looking for an affordable and efficient laptop. Whether you need it for office work, entertainment, or web browsing, this laptop provides the power to do more.', '9876568890', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dswzvbhix/image/upload/v1740654814/cysfcuaouzemcfirz1yo.png', '2025-02-27 11:13:35'),
